a minute some similarities

00:28:05.250 --> 00:28:10.640 position:56%
that can easily be translated to and
help in fact address human cancers.

00:28:10.640 --> 00:28:12.600
And there's a benefit because
it's a win on both sides

00:28:12.600 --> 00:28:15.460
when we can have interventions
through drugs,

00:28:15.460 --> 00:28:18.000
surgery for pets as
well as for people.

00:28:18.000 --> 00:28:19.300
And right now we have

00:28:19.300 --> 00:28:22.780
