00:30:35.440 --> 00:30:36.740
Well, they have 20 copies.

00:30:36.740 --> 00:30:38.040
But guess what?

00:30:38.040 --> 00:30:39.340
You and I only have one.

00:30:39.340 --> 00:30:41.170
Is that possibly why?

00:30:41.170 --> 00:30:43.060
It's most interesting to see that.

00:30:43.060 --> 00:30:46.050
So once again, understanding
