00:38:20.320 --> 00:38:22.680
surveillance effort
to combat resistance.

00:38:22.680 --> 00:38:26.500
Again, we do need to study this,
we need to be surveilling this,

00:38:26.500 --> 00:38:29.300
and we need to be able to
accelerate the research

00:38:29.300 --> 00:38:30.940
to give us the tools that we need.

00:38:30.940 --> 00:38:33.540
Potentially even vaccines
can help as well here.

00:38:33.540 --> 00:38:36.250
But it's also going to improve
international collaboration

00:38:36.250 --> 00:38:41.000
and sharing of information
that we see.

