00:52:12.490 --> 00:52:15.380
Anthrax was used here
up on the Hill.

00:52:15.380 --> 00:52:19.520
The potential for some
of these viruses is huge.

00:52:19.520 --> 00:52:23.510
It's that awareness
again of why nations need

00:52:23.510 --> 00:52:27.210
to understand the devastation
that would occur

00:52:27.210 --> 00:52:29.860
through a biological agent
that if that transmission,

00:52:29.860 --> 00:52:33.390
especially being transmitted from
people to people for example,

00:52:33.390 --> 00:52:37.540
is huge, then in this global world,

00:52:37.540 --> 00:52:40.330
it doesn't take much
to have that spread.

00:52:40.330 --> 00:52:44.640
And that annihilation is
horrific to even think about it.

00:52:44.640 --> 00:52:49.830
So it think it's more
important, and this is why as even

00:52:49.830 --> 00:52:54.100
with the nuclear weapon discussion,
the devastation is so huge,

00:52:54.100 --> 00:52:58.810
everybody needs to do everything
they can to prevent that.

00:52:58.810 --> 00:53:05.000
So the education of what
these biological viruses

00:53:05.000 --> 00:53:10.410
and agents can do is one that
we would hope would be forefront

00:53:10.410 --> 00:53:17.150
and the government agencies to
say we're not going to go there.

00:53:17.150 --> 00:53:24.750
A lot of good can come from so
much of the research that we have,

00:53:24.750 --> 00:53:33.440
and the understanding of so many
of these important entities.

00:53:33.440 --> 00:53:35.670
But you're right.

00:53:35.670 --> 00:53:47.290
You flip the coin and they can
suddenly become the most horrific

00:53:47.290 --> 00:53:54.590
agents that we've ever seen if
we don't have a way to intervene.

00:53:54.590 --> 00:54:07.570
For some of these agents, we
may or may not have a treatment

00:54:07.570 --> 00:54:10.020
or a vaccine, and how
long does it take

00:54:10.020 --> 00:54:14.540
to develop those interventions,
is it a challenge?

00:54:14.540 --> 00:54:18.270
And then how do you stockpile
so that you're prepared?

00:54:18.270 --> 00:54:19.570
So I agree with you.

00:54:19.570 --> 00:54:22.560
I would hope that our nations
internationally can work together

00:54:22.560 --> 00:54:27.460 position:56%
and avoid going there, but it's only
through that heightened awareness.

00:54:27.460 --> 00:54:32.210 position:56%
And that gets back again to then how
do you do the surveillance to track

00:54:32.210 --> 00:54:37.130
and see what's happening, and
only through us acknowledging

00:54:37.130 --> 00:54:39.330
that we do live together
in this world.

00:54:39.330 --> 00:54:42.000
So what's going to happen just

00:54:42.000 --> 00:54:43.700
across the ocean can
still impact us.

00:54:43.700 --> 00:54:49.670
That mindset, I think is
starting to change more and more.

00:54:49.670 --> 00:54:52.050
That's a good question.

00:54:52.050 --> 00:54:53.350
Thank you.

00:54:53.350 --> 00:54:54.650
Yes, ma'am.

00:54:54.650 --> 00:54:55.950
&gt;&gt; Does FDA have any
cooperative programs

00:54:55.950 --> 00:54:58.700
where they assist developing
countries with developing processes

00:54:58.700 --> 00:55:01.170
for drug approvals or for
diagnostic test approvals?

00:55:01.170 --> 00:55:04.730 position:56%
I mean, there are a lot of neglected
[inaudible] diseases out there

00:55:04.730 --> 00:55:08.610
that we don't have here, therefore,
there's no incentive for a lot

00:55:08.610 --> 00:55:09.910
of [inaudible] activity here.

00:55:09.910 --> 00:55:12.040
But certainly FDA has expertise
that could be shared by helping

00:55:12.040 --> 00:55:13.400
out countries that do
have these problems.

00:55:13.400 --> 00:55:14.700
&gt;&gt; Bernadette Dunham: The question
is does FDA have programs whereby

00:55:14.700 --> 00:55:16.000
the staff that has
this knowledgebase

00:55:16.000 --> 00:55:17.300
of the drug approval process,
can they assist other countries

00:55:17.300 --> 00:55:18.710
where in fact they do have diseases
that we might not have here,

00:55:18.710 --> 00:55:20.010
and can they assist
in developing programs

00:55:20.010 --> 00:55:21.310
for drug approval in
the other countries.

00:55:21.310 --> 00:55:22.610
And there's a number
of groups where we look

00:55:22.610 --> 00:55:23.910
at international harmonization
literally for human drugs

00:55:23.910 --> 00:55:25.210
and animal drugs on how
countries can share information

00:55:25.210 --> 00:55:26.780
and work together and have the
pharmaceutical companies literally

00:55:26.780 --> 00:55:28.080
be able to go through
the process of bringing

00:55:28.080 --> 00:55:29.380
to fruition approved products
in different countries,

00:55:29.380 --> 00:55:30.680
taking advantage of
that knowledgebase.

00:55:30.680 --> 00:55:32.030
Many times, we have workshops and
sessions to go to other countries

00:55:32.030 --> 00:55:34.040 position:56%
to showcase examples of how they can
develop their own regulatory program

00:55:34.040 --> 00:55:35.340
for drug approval.

00:55:35.340 --> 00:55:36.640
And the companies themselves
often participate

00:55:36.640 --> 00:55:37.940
to enhance that awareness.

00:55:37.940 --> 00:55:39.240
Wherever we can, I think the
part that's so critical --

00:55:39.240 --> 00:55:40.540
and we see this even with HIV --

00:55:40.540 --> 00:55:41.840
so we have potential products
that can be used to treat people,

00:55:41.840 --> 00:55:43.140
but then how do we make those
available and affordable

00:55:43.140 --> 00:55:44.440
when you're looking
across the world?

00:55:44.440 --> 00:55:45.740
And that's going to bring
the countries together

00:55:45.740 --> 00:55:47.040
to address these issues as well.

00:55:47.040 --> 00:55:48.340
So there is that capability.

00:55:48.340 --> 00:55:49.640
And a number of governments
will come here and visit with us

00:55:49.640 --> 00:55:50.940
and learn how do you do A, B, C, D,

00:55:50.940 --> 00:55:52.240 position:56%
E. And if we can show them different
venues at different levels --

00:55:52.240 --> 00:55:53.540
so what exactly do you need?

00:55:53.540 --> 00:55:54.840
It may not be the same as a
different country over here.

00:55:54.840 --> 00:55:56.140
You may want the full
monty; you may not.

00:55:56.140 --> 00:55:57.440
And we can help, and
other countries can help

00:55:57.440 --> 00:55:58.740
that have full regulatory programs
onboard to work with countries

00:55:58.740 --> 00:56:00.040
that are coming forward
and developing their own.

00:56:00.040 --> 00:56:01.340
Thank you.

